description:
LibriVox recording of Her Dark Inheritance by Mrs. E. Burke Collins.

Read in English by Sharon Kilmer

A story of obsessive love and desperation that hid many secrets. This cliffhanger will keep you guessing until the very end. Summary by Sharon Kilmer
